            <title><![CDATA[B&amp;Y Ventures launches Lebanon&#039;s first Angel Investor Network]]></title>
                        <description><![CDATA[<ul>
	<li>B&amp;Y Venture&nbsp;Partners has launched the Lebanese Angel Investor Network (LAIN), a curated angel investment network targeting Lebanese and diaspora-founded startups, supported by Lebanon&#39;s Ministry of Technology and Artificial Intelligence (MITAI).&nbsp;</li>
	<li>The network said it secured commitments exceeding its initial target shortly after launch, without revealing the investment amount or investors&#39; identities.</li>
	<li>LAIN introduced its first cohort of startup opportunities through the Vessel platform, featuring four curated Lebanese founders.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Press release:</strong></p>

<p>B&amp;Y Venture&nbsp;Partners has launched the Lebanese Angel Investor Network (LAIN),&nbsp;opening&nbsp;commitments for investors and&nbsp;marking a new step toward strengthening Lebanon&rsquo;s early-stage startup investment ecosystem.</p>

<p>The network announced that it had already secured commitments exceeding its initial target shortly after launch, reflecting strong interest from the local and diaspora investment community.</p>

<p>The launch event featured opening remarks from Lebanon&rsquo;s Minister Kamal Shehadi, who outlined MITAI Lebanon&rsquo;s vision for positioning Lebanon as a digital republic and supporting innovation-driven economic growth.</p>

<p>According to the organisers, the launch also introduced LAIN&rsquo;s first cohort of potential startup investments via the Vessel platform. The initial group includes four curated founders and startup opportunities identified through the network and the broader Lebanese diaspora ecosystem.</p>

<p>LAIN aims to create a structured angel investment platform that connects Lebanese founders and early-stage startups with investors, mentors, and strategic networks across Lebanon and internationally.</p>

<p>The network said it is now officially accepting investor commitments through its online platform as it begins building its first investment pipeline.</p>]]></description>
